{
  "id": "RAW_c33cfc",
  "title": "GPT-4o 整活！3 个小时、6 个镜头重现吉卜力版《甄嬛传》名场面",
  "url": "https://www.jiqizhixin.com/articles/2025-03-28-12",
  "date": "2025-03-28 11:10:00",
  "author": "AI好好用",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2c42bda-362f-4e74-08bc-a9a9d2c81800/public\" alt=\"ChatGPT Image 2025年3月28日 11_14_23.png\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044028\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3376d8bb-d62c-4500-be39-a602586e42ad/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">编辑 | 杨文</strong></p>\n  <p>网友整的花样可真够多的。</p>\n  <p>自打 GPT-4o 上线文生图模型以来，我的朋友圈就被它刷了屏。</p>\n  <p>有人用来搞漫画：</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d1004b2-79b3-4a50-0bfa-347b1c658e00/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" data-imgfileid=\"100044027\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3e67d989-f46a-4644-b69d-fb2aecca28cb/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>有人拿它玩梗图：</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e095010f-3d7a-4657-5228-eab0901c4100/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044029\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/a97d67bf-dfe3-4316-8c0c-19e3f4fc3b48/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>最最绝的是，有网友直接让它整活影视剧名场面。</p>\n  <p>比如吉卜力风格的《星际穿越》，完美复刻出电影中的玉米地、被海洋覆盖的米勒星球以及那个名叫 TARS 的机器人。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6VFtMDqz0F-u3gxdjEaltw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/c4933daf-aaeb-4829-b838-f4a78c4d9101/1743160322071.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <section>\n   <span data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FDT8udUick9sJ6PDZQLvFIJx2weJsYZ3YFNl2EvFzmjIYuJyBWYtoSVwYlO2zicWicH49WTI5r07u9QcM3YGNXa3gA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3917135207647674385\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3917135207647674385\" data-vh=\"369.703125\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-vw=\"657.25\" height=\"384\" scrolling=\"no\" width=\"661\"></span><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">视频来自：X 博主 @kb24x7&nbsp;</span>\n  </section>\n  <p>据作者介绍，他是使用 GPT-4o 和 Morphic 两款工具制作而成。</p>\n  <p>先是截取电影中的经典镜头，然后使用 GPT-4o 将每一帧画面转绘成吉卜力风格，再在 Morphic 这款 AI 视频工具将风格化后的图片变成视频，最后剪辑在一起即可。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/900dd7f2-0130-41fb-8a2f-13cb1fdcdc00/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.8611111111111112\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044030\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/43d633fd-9548-4b2f-9946-a8d2bbc49906/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"3\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>X 博主 @PJaccetturo 则制作了一版吉卜力风格的《魔戒》预告片，效果也是杠杠滴：</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6VFtMDqz0F-u3gxdjEaltw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/8faa3c8c-291d-48d2-9de0-e536d5e8ef77/1743160343773.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <section>\n   <span data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FDT8udUick9sKZyUNKCbaKwiaYSW5shwYCce8QUDexWRXaTzklWlGKYVgutS23iaWZJVGjwBxna10ibicAA4fiaoY0dUg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3918572537982189577\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3918572537982189577\" data-vh=\"492.9375\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-vw=\"657.25\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"508\" scrolling=\"no\" width=\"661\"></span>他花了整整 9 个小时，费了 250 美元的 Kling 点数才制作出这不到 2 分钟的动画预告片。\n  </section>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e1a28d75-86cb-443a-6b18-5759010c9b00/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.17962962962962964\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044035\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/4a922a9c-fc00-49a9-8bee-b730316d64ce/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"5\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>不过，他并没有使用 GPT-4o，而是用了 OpenAI 的 Sora 工具，将官方预告片中的 102 个镜头转绘成吉卜力动画风格。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/68b0913d-19c6-49be-eaf5-2a9db90ef300/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.8740740740740741\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044036\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f27dad44-e642-46ca-84f9-5229deabaa21/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"6\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>在转绘风格时，博主输入的提示词：「请以吉卜力工作室的风格重新绘制这张图片，画面精致细腻，并保持原图的构图、色彩和氛围。图中的场景是几个穿黑斗篷的骑士骑着黑马，在一条河床上疾驰，而他们的身后，巨大的水浪正疯狂地追逐着他们。」&nbsp;</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/efea00ed-6867-4333-8589-f94e00caf300/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.7638888888888888\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044037\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/7ff27476-ab6e-40e3-b59c-b408726061aa/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"4\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>当然，如果使用 GPT-4o，效果也将不遑多让。</p>\n  <p>该博主也坦言，由于时间有限，他并未给动画角色对口型，而是在 Kling AI 和 Luma AI 中使用了简单的提示词，例如：「一个男人惊恐地喊叫」、「一个女人面带忧虑地说话，眉头紧锁」 。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4c31fe71-6637-4c08-ea4f-d1a04c8c7300/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.9027777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044038\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/eb14c5a0-fc1b-4973-8a8d-f390dfb190fe/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"7\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>如此有趣，我们也来凑个热闹。</p>\n  <p>用 GPT-4o 和可灵攒了一个吉卜力版的《甄嬛传》经典桥段：臣妾要告发熹贵妃私通，秽乱后宫，罪不容诛……</p>\n  <p>其制作也相当简单，总共就三步。</p>\n  <p>第一步：截镜头 + GPT-4o 转绘</p>\n  <p>找到《甄嬛传》中祺贵人告发熹贵妃的片段，截取其中几个关键的镜头。</p>\n  <p>由于时间原因，我只截取了 6 帧画面。即使画质糊一些也没关系，GPT-4o 可以精准识别并自动提升画质。</p>\n  <section data-id=\"86426\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n   <section data-role=\"animate\">\n    <section>\n     <section data-svg-role=\"block\" data-width=\"600%\">\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7e8933f2-0708-49e0-45ed-07432bda8700/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.5642201834862385\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"872\" data-imgfileid=\"100044064\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"9\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/44326747-ec5b-4b62-9922-50a42c6b59b9/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"9\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fdcf81da-17fa-44d5-aaeb-c4bcf3bc5e00/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.5593607305936074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"876\" data-imgfileid=\"100044063\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"10\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/bb64911d-f74e-41d5-a147-39c40eeee11b/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"8\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/694d6272-aca4-4c2b-879e-7c4d31fd1b00/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.5639269406392694\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"876\" data-imgfileid=\"100044066\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"11\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/75a8d1af-6505-4fd8-92fe-a41cf036a0c6/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"20\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2386eadb-8f16-487b-4fc5-7bf632887200/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.5642201834862385\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"872\" data-imgfileid=\"100044067\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"12\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ea1a2b9e-c594-4ac0-ba73-defa6c00d5a4/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"22\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23a30d70-7c76-4d69-a2ad-521928db6c00/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.5606407322654462\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"874\" data-imgfileid=\"100044065\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"13\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0b51ea76-c303-45c2-b6e7-7f1484265144/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"19\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/75b1e3d6-0fe5-4ea3-2730-97e525e06500/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.5558086560364465\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"878\" data-imgfileid=\"100044068\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"14\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/5439924b-97eb-4bb8-9128-2fdb24d7fd1a/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"21\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>然后，将这些画面逐一上传至 GPT-4o，并输入提示词：「请帮我把这张照片转成吉卜力风格」。\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f991bf82-5bf2-4951-3f62-a0e4a2b56400/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.475\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044040\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"15\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/e2fe3519-6de5-4ddc-a3b0-1d6d77ac9473/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"10\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p>只需静待一小会儿，GPT-4o 就能将它们转绘成吉卜力风格，都几乎不用抽卡，一次就能成功。</p>\n  <section data-id=\"86426\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n   <section data-role=\"animate\">\n    <section>\n     <section data-svg-role=\"block\" data-width=\"600%\">\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/357c22a5-4fdc-48df-b39c-324790c89200/public\" alt=\"ChatGPT Image 2025年3月28日 11_08_15.png\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044047\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"16\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f6136b7e-8bce-40d4-b6cf-9f968de8c432/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"11\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7def5cb0-42d7-44cd-b1bf-0b6575a56b00/public\" alt=\"ChatGPT Image 2025年3月28日 11_14_23.png\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044044\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"17\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f67d08bb-2ff7-44d6-9d7f-6b4a06c949fb/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"15\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a14f41d0-6404-4e2f-3814-b89fda579400/public\" alt=\"ChatGPT Image 2025年3月28日 11_31_52.png\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044045\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"18\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0a778266-242b-41df-b8d7-8527949f1d48/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"16\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d3603761-8079-401d-d20c-718945039b00/public\" alt=\"ChatGPT Image 2025年3月28日 11_38_51.png\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044046\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"19\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/d8706124-0e29-4f42-9867-2ea91dfc4382/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"13\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3dab26c4-ae4c-4073-9677-e52ebb595000/public\" alt=\"ChatGPT Image 2025年3月28日 11_38_43.png\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044043\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"20\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/8ecf2db8-ca9b-4c3f-856f-200d9c463d87/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"12\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"16.66%\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bfa09bfe-2d6f-4e38-2bba-6d4c3b965800/public\" alt=\"ChatGPT Image 2025年3月28日 11_51_18.png\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044048\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-index=\"21\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/47bccd3c-ab1c-4a42-80d9-007dcd349994/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"14\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section data-svg-blockname=\"描述性文字\" data-svg-op=\"delete\" data-svg-role=\"block\">\n     <p>左右滑动查看更多</p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p>第二步：图片转视频。</p>\n  <p>接下来的操作也是重头戏，需要将风格化后的图片动起来。</p>\n  <p>我们使用的工具则是可灵 1.6 模型的「图生视频」功能，上传图片，再输入提示词即可。</p>\n  <p>值得一提的是，在进行提示词描述时，不要太复杂，最好简洁而准确地给出人物、动作和神态，比如这个女人在大声说话，神情严肃。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/90e72fc7-7b31-4a4a-695d-528d75f16600/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"1.3643724696356276\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"988\" data-imgfileid=\"100044049\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"22\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/bcfc9d47-c417-4ab4-bfd5-2abbf52cb711/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"17\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>我们实测了这 6 个镜头，发现相比之前的模型，可灵 1.6 模型有了较大的进步，人物动作更加流畅，生成的画面也更加稳定。</p>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p>不过，在生成熹贵妃的手指突然抠桌角这一幕时，可灵还是会有些瑕疵，比如穿戴甲突然消失，或者手指缺失等，多抽卡几次直至得到好的结果为止。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6VFtMDqz0F-u3gxdjEaltw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0a929c89-3092-45fa-84e2-b226cb8a6bfc/1743160141703.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <section>\n   <span data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FDT8udUick9sKZyUNKCbaKwiaYSW5shwYCcxxRmXdtMB39hdrktkm2ic2ibo9TuNiaJcp8ksxroAicxPrTicGlWqWvaQpw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3918586188294144006\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3918586188294144006\" data-vh=\"369.703125\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-vw=\"657.25\" height=\"384\" scrolling=\"no\" width=\"661\"></span>第三步：剪辑。\n  </section>\n  <p>我们先把原视频和生成好的素材全部导入剪映中。</p>\n  <p>然后使用剪映的「音频分离」功能，将原视频中的音频摘出来，再根据音频进行吉卜力风格的素材剪辑即可。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6e38f1e7-82ae-43db-ed98-79b7bf76b700/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.7148148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044058\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"23\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/9e6cb9f5-c6eb-49c8-8df0-8e76878291f9/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"18\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>来看看效果：</p>\n  <section>\n   <div tabindex=\"0\" title=\"轻点两下前往视频号\">\n    <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6VFtMDqz0F-u3gxdjEaltw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/8c62af79-0c4e-4911-b45c-270b6ed4c186/1743160177418.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a>\n   </div>\n   <div tabindex=\"0\" title=\"轻点两下前往视频号\">\n    工具链接：\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <p>GPT-4o 链接：https://chatgpt.com/</p>\n  <p>可灵 AI 链接：https://app.klingai.com/</p>\n  <p>剪映</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   以后我们会带来更多好玩有用的 AI 评测，也欢迎大家进群交流。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ba42770c-0a5e-4e3d-32f9-b33dcebba500/public\" data-ratio=\"1.0010649627263046\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"939\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044059\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"24\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/4c9c828e-928e-487a-841d-abd6bf6276a5/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"23\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文展示了如何利用 GPT-4o 和可灵等 AI 工具，快速低成本地将影视剧片段转换成吉卜力动画风格，《甄嬛传》案例提供了具体制作流程。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文展示了如何利用 GPT-4o 和可灵等 AI 工具，快速低成本地将影视剧片段转换成吉卜力动画风格，《甄嬛传》案例提供了具体制作流程。",
  "summary": "文章主要介绍了如何利用 GPT-4o 和可灵 AI 工具，将影视剧片段转换成吉卜力动画风格。通过截取电影或电视剧的关键镜头，使用 GPT-4o 进行风格转换，再利用可灵 AI 的图生视频功能生成动画片段，最后通过剪映等工具进行剪辑，即可完成制作。文章展示了 GPT-4o 和可灵 AI 结合使用的便捷性和趣味性，为 AI 内容创作提供了一种新思路。《甄嬛传》案例详细展示了整个制作流程，降低了动画制作的门槛，让更多人可以参与到创意内容生产中。",
